import React, { Fragment } from "react"
import Card from '@material-ui/core/Card'
import Body1 from 'ui/atom/typography/body1'
import {TPostProps} from 'type/post'

const PostCard: React.FC<TPostProps> = props => {
    return (
        <Fragment>
            <Card key={props.id}>
                <Body1>{props.title}</Body1>
                <Body1>{props.isFavorite}</Body1>
            </Card>
        </Fragment>
    )
}
export default PostCard
